be kept a close eye on just now.

17:18.436 --> 17:21.473
But she's fine.
She's always been the life and soul.

17:21.517 --> 17:25.066
Tabasco in your pint, frisbee in the
kitchen, that's Merry. She's kooky.

17:25.117 --> 17:27.790
