18:56.638 --> 18:58.230
Tightly tied.

18:58.278 --> 19:01.634
I appreciate how passionately
you feel about your friend

19:01.678 --> 19:05.034
but there's no way I can sign her out.
I'm sorry.

19:05.078 --> 19:08.115
Look, Merry wanted me
to give you these deeds.

19:08.158 --> 19:12.276
I'm not sure why or what...

19:12.318 --> 19:15.754
